  <summary date="2021-05-14T23:20:09Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Educational Equity Challenge Grant Act of 2021

This bill establishes a program through which the Department of Education must award grants to eligible entities (e.g., state and local educational agencies) to address students' academic, social, emotional, mental, behavioral, and physical health needs related to the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic.</summary>
